{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7357230489","title":"右派言论——反对苏联  宣扬资本主义","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bed939f113","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"7357230489"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5378a8871a","name":"学生"},{"id":"5841b1c66b","name":"上海财经学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"990bacbcef","type":"title","text":"右派言论——反对苏联  宣扬资本主义","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"95df733628","type":"authors","text":"上海财经学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"db4f530519","type":"subtitle","text":"(一)污蔑苏联  破坏社会主义团结","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"18659cad74","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“马林科夫反党集团的出现，只有社会主义国家才有，资本主义国家不会有。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"ac94ff92d5","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“赫鲁晓夫一派人排挤斯大林一派。赫鲁晓夫是乌克兰人，斯大林一派不是，所以要排挤。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"227cc0b829","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“我们估计在批评斯大林错误后，苏共中央有新旧两派势力在剧烈的斗争。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"336e40adef","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“苏联建国四十年还出现马林科夫反党集团，这是宗派主义。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"7a1313b4d7","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“托洛斯基等争夺领导权，斯大林把他开除；苏共对马林科夫的问题，不能肯定没有争权夺利。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"b45b57b95c","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)看到萨布罗夫等撤职后说：“布尔加宁也靠不住，列宁死后斯大林与另二个叫什么夫的争权夺利，930个中央委员中枪决390多个。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"23dda13c6a","type":"paragraph","text":"(7)“米高扬在十九大会上一口一个‘斯大林英明伟大’。而现在二十大会上则说：斯大林如何不好，又是个人崇拜，又是个人英雄主义。这是拍马屁，简直是混帐。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"903629401c","type":"paragraph","text":"(8)“苏联干涉匈牙利内政。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"0f5d3a1a1e","type":"paragraph","text":"(9)“匈牙利反革命问题是苏联革命输出，不符合马克思理论。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"2e1ed9f760","type":"paragraph","text":"(10)“苏联出兵是多管闲事、干涉、侵略。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"8a6df236f6","type":"paragraph","text":"(11)“苏联派一个苏联人在波兰当国防部长(指罗科索夫斯基)，是苏联大国沙文主义的表现，这象什么话?”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"89f5e7c82a","type":"paragraph","text":"(12)“苏联和南斯拉夫的关系上，南斯拉夫能坚持原则。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"06b3cb8d8e","type":"paragraph","text":"(13)“爱沙尼亚、拉脱维亚、立陶宛三个加盟共和国加入苏联是强迫的，是大国沙文主义的表现。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"424c7b3e74","type":"paragraph","text":"(14)“苏联和阿富汗边境事件，很多都是苏联不对。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"7f1c2a94be","type":"paragraph","text":"(15)“苏联在中国新疆和中国合资经营的石油公司，还得利润，这是大国主义。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"e8f89bf982","type":"paragraph","text":"(16)“抗日时期苏联解放东北后拆走一部分机器，现在苏联支援我们是应该的，这就是归还我们的财产。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"189ebecafa","type":"paragraph","text":"(17)“海参崴以前就是我们的，为什么现在属于苏联了。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"f6f9a55f0e","type":"paragraph","text":"(18)“蒙古人民共和国是外蒙古，应该属于我们中国的本土，苏联帮助蒙古独立这是侵犯行为。”","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"51bb67dce9","type":"paragraph","text":"(19)“苏军驻旅大的军队纪律不严，乱搞男女关系。”","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"29a0fb1399","type":"paragraph","text":"(20)×××统购统销时说：“好肉好米我们吃不到，都被老大哥吃掉了。”","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"c505f1b0f1","type":"paragraph","text":"(21)“中国的高等学校中有苏联顾问，这是苏联与人民民主国家有些不平等。”","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"bec7eb1a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"(22)“这样盛大的欢迎伏老是浪费，现在节约时期为什么又把儿子媳妇都带来，这是列宁的叛徒。”","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"28601e846a","type":"paragraph","text":"(23)“中国真是没有一点民族自尊心，连上海交响乐团总指挥这么一点小事情都要苏联来领导。”","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"6f0122ed61","type":"paragraph","text":"(24)“苏联电影不值得我国来放映，水平太低。”","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"bfa8c91136","type":"paragraph","text":"(25)苏联伏老来访问我国时，×××说：“我不听外国佬的讲话。”","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"ee37df50da","type":"subtitle","text":"(二)宣扬资本主义","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"a056531317","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“美国导弹比苏联强，美国试验了几次氢弹，而苏联就没有试验；美国也有‘喀秋莎’，比苏联还要好；美国原子武器多，还有原子步枪。”","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"06b965f478","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“美国的武器好，精小，苏联武器粗笨。”","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"1ab7eaf8b4","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“美国包围着我们，他们空军多么强大，海军有多么大的航空母舰。”","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"f17bfa8cc7","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“美国大学是世界上第一流的，中国的大学根本比不上美国。”","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"b8c723657d","type":"paragraph","text":"(5)“帝国主义对中国侵略，中国是有好处的，尤其对中国工业发展是有帮助的，……否则中国在技术上不会有这样好的。”","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"3ff7be59a0","type":"paragraph","text":"(6)“中国政府没收帝国主义国家财产是不合理的。”","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"de6f0c77d2","type":"subtitle","text":"三、其他","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"df31a8f4e2","type":"paragraph","text":"(1)“希特勒卐字国徽从艺术观点上说是世界上最美的。”","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"c47f954d87","type":"paragraph","text":"(2)“浙江奉化出了两个大名人，一是蒋介石，一是张××(指他自己)。”","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"d2832536fb","type":"paragraph","text":"(3)“中国人民大学是教条主义大本营，教条主义都是从那里来的。”","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"03da9efc6f","type":"paragraph","text":"(4)“外国人说中国大学生没头脑，盲目跟共产党走。”","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"},{"id":"653adcda31","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《反右派斗争言论选辑　第一辑　学生部份》（中共上海财经学院委员会编，1957年9","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489"}],"page":{"id":"1dff1fa4be","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"7357230489","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}